data.description: Splish! Splash! Dreaming of having your own pool? Here is your chance! This immaculate ranch is located near West Point Lake, Industrial Park, Okfuskee Event Center, and a few miles from KIA. This home features granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, sliding shelves, a breakfast bar, breakfast area, and a dining room. Laminate floors throughout and tile in the bathrooms. Has a cozy fireplace in the living room. Spacious master suite with trey ceilings and a walk- in closet. Freshly remodeled master bathroom with a custom tile shower and double vanities. Enjoy sitting on your screened porch overlooking your in-ground pool. Fenced yard with a pergola and a parking area for an RV. Has an out building and a large back yard that is ideal for a big shop. Beautiful flowers that bloom in the spring. Roof is only a few years old! A must see!
